##  <Oper Name="LogFFE" Arg='z, r'/>
##
##  <Description>
##  <Ref Func="LogFFE"/> returns the discrete logarithm of the element
##  <A>z</A> in a finite field with respect to the root <A>r</A>.
##  An error is signalled if <A>z</A> is zero.
